---
import Section from "../ui/Section.astro";
---

<Section id="method" title="The method (why it’s different)">
  <div class="grid grid--2">
    <div class="card step">
      <p class="step__kicker">Step 1</p>
      <h3 class="step__h">Tongue posture</h3>
      <p class="muted">Learn placement and cues that support facial structure (placeholder).</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card step">
      <p class="step__kicker">Step 2</p>
      <h3 class="step__h">Breathing</h3>
      <p class="muted">Reduce shallow patterns and support better posture (placeholder).</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card step">
      <p class="step__kicker">Step 3</p>
      <h3 class="step__h">Soft tissue work</h3>
      <p class="muted">Gentle release + activation to reduce tension (placeholder).</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card step">
      <p class="step__kicker">Step 4</p>
      <h3 class="step__h">Consistency</h3>
      <p class="muted">A short routine you can repeat daily — without equipment.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .step__kicker {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(238, 240, 255, 0.65);
    }
    .step__h { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .step p { margin: 0; }
  </style>
</Section>
